<sect1 version="5.0" xml:lang="en" xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook"
		>
	<title>Validating a project</title>

	<para>
		The forge administrator validates the projects. Simply go to the
		navigation menu and choose
		<emphasis role="bold">FIXME Validate projects.</emphasis>
	</para>

	<figure>
		<title>Validate project menu</title>

		<mediaobject>
			<imageobject>
				<imagedata align="center" fileref="04-02-01-ValidateProjectMenu.png"
					width="250px" />
			</imageobject>
		</mediaobject>
	</figure>

	<para>After starting the application, choose the project to be
		validated and click the validation button. The following figure shows
		the project validation screen:</para>

	<figure>
		<title>Validate project</title>

		<mediaobject>
			<imageobject>
				<imagedata align="center" fileref="04-02-02-ValidateProject.png" />
			</imageobject>
		</mediaobject>
	</figure>
</sect1>
